Ryo is supposed to be back later today, so if he gets back, the CATs 
are his once again.


::Killfest/Dark/Liono::

Killfest is sent flying backwards along with Motormaster when the 
other hurtles into him. He pushes away, the zero gravity of space 
allowing fairly easy manuevering. He looks up in time to see a plasma 
shot from Dark Convoy heading for him. Killfest lifts his arms, 
blocking the shot but flying backwards from the impact.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Liono smiles, although in pain, seeing Motormaster hurtle into 
Killfest. He aims at Motormaster again, firing a fireball.
